mermaid
graph TB
    Client["Client / cURL"] -->|POST /api/v1/jobs| API["HTTP API (Gin)"]
    API -->|INSERT status=pending| PG[("PostgreSQL")]
    API -->|Publish JobMessage| MQ["RabbitMQ\n(jobs queue)"]
    MQ -->|Consume| WP["Worker Pool\n(N goroutines)"]
    WP -->|FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED| PG
    WP -->|UPDATE status| PG
    WP -->|Failed > maxRetries| DLQ["Dead Letter Queue\n(jobs.dlq)"]
    WP -->|Metrics| PROM["Prometheus"]
    PROM --> GRAFANA["Grafana Dashboard"]
    API -->|GET /dashboard| DASH["Dashboard UI (SSE)"]
    DASH -->|poll stats| PG
